{
  "texts": [
    "\"Do you understand how to use this function, or would you like me to explain it to you again\"? vi.",
    "Phrasing output format: One can instruct ChatGPT to present its responses in various formats, such as bullet points, paragraphs, or tables.",
    "Utilising bullet points is particularly effective for presenting sequential instructions in a clear and easy-to-follow manner.",
    "For instance, in this study, we guided ChatGPT to rephrase its output by instructing it to; \"Please use bullet points to list the steps for activating or deactivating any function\".",
    "In our experimental setup, we designed a unique user manual, approximately 1,100 words in length, detailing the location and function of each ADAS feature."
  ]
}